task.summary: Completed base version of compose function for Pentiga objects. Added custom function scaling across bands for Pentiga structures. Started building Pentara test cases.
Separated Pentara and Pentiga classes in file structure. Started Pentiga testing file. Added todo notes for Pentara objects. Updated Pentara.__init__.py to include Pentara and Pentiga objects.
Set test array in test_data folder, made updates and cleanups in pentara_tests.py
Reformatted pentiga_tests.py, changed imports and set todo tests

Added test cases and test data files in /test_data/ sub-directory. Separated testing scripts of Pentiga objects to pentiga_scratch. Renamed some functions in Pentiga objects now includes band-wise, coordinate-wise, and band-coord-wise functions for Pentiga structure scaling.

Additional testing for Pentiga functions. Modifications to pentiga functions and additional documentation. Added additional test arrays in hsi_atk/test_data for pentiga tests. Fixed loadBIL from /dataset.py
Minor restructuring. Started functions for Pentiga labels.
Specializing for hsi kernel analysis. Merge later as child classes
Fixed labeling to access labels dictionary for pentigas
Added structure for pentiga labeling functions via arbitrary functions.
Changed adding pentiga structures to adding by pentiga compose() func
Edit for bandwidth specifications of pentiga structures, compose() edits, substructure generators, and labeling functions
Finished basic version of pentiga generator function with multiple structures, scaling, and labels.
